OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChinese cities sinking     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Funder their own weight     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Nearly half of China's major cities are
OL,6, sinking because of water extraction and
OL,7, the increasing weight of their rapid   
OL,8, expansion, researchers say.            
OL,10,FSome cities are subsiding rapidly, with
OL,11,Fone in six exceeding 10mm per year.    
OL,13,FChina's rapid urbanisation in recent   
OL,14,Fdecades means far more water is now    
OL,15,Fbeing drawn up to meet people's needs, 
OL,16,Fscientists say.                        
OL,18,FIn coastal cities, this subsidence     
OL,19,Fthreatens millions of people with      
OL,20,Fflooding as sea levels rise.           
